column5: I have Tuesday Afternoon off and want to try some of the Laker\Whitie action I keep hearing about I'd be coming from just North of Barrie if anyone wants to join. Let me know!
If i leave now...i might just make it!  By the looks of the fishing on Simcoe i'd love to join ya...but i'm a bit fa away.   Good luck and tight lines for Tuesday
I'll pick you up and we'll be there by next Tuesday.....
